# Unit Tests Directory

This directory contains unit tests for individual classes and methods.
Unit tests should be isolated and not depend on WordPress or external services.

## Structure:
- ModelsTest/ - Tests for data models
- ServicesTest/ - Tests for service layer
- UtilsTest/ - Tests for utility functions
- ApiTest/ - Tests for API client classes

## Naming Convention:
- Test files should end with `Test.php`
- Test classes should end with `Test`
- Test methods should start with `test`

## Example:
```php
<?php
namespace Bil24\Tests\Unit;

use PHPUnit\Framework\TestCase;
use Bil24\Models\Event;

class EventTest extends TestCase {
    public function testEventCreation() {
        // Test implementation
    }
}
``` 